{
  "stem": "9701.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe they see two students fighting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have a choice to make.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They can walk past and ignore it, or maybe they can intervene.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it may seem it's a small thing, but it's-- we all need to do that to make this world a better world, not only for others, but in the process for ourselves also.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did go back to Germany in July of 1945, not as I had originally planned, to re-educate the Germans, but I was fortunate enough to obtain employment with the American government.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked for the US Civil Censorship division for one year in Munich, Germany, censoring incoming and outgoing German mail.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my intention was when my contract is over, my one-year contract is over, I will then stay in Germany as I had planned.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- that's not what happened, though.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the train stopped in Germany the first time as I was returning, there were children on the platform begging for chewing gum and candy, cookies, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were people on the train just like I, refugees from Germany, Austria, Czechoslovakia, going back to Germany to work for the American government.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some of them gave these children whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I just became absolutely livid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How dare you give something to these Nazis?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of these so-called Nazis were, you know, five years old maybe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I could-- I-- I was not aware until that moment that I had such anger and such hatred within me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was not able to rationalize that these children are not guilty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They've not done anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it took me quite a while before I was able to get over this hatred for everybody who was German.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
